    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complex Combat</h2>Interstellar warfare is more complex than larger numbers beating smaller ones. A commander must always consider the weapons of enemy systems, the strength of each side’s probes in flight, and openings you may be creating for your opponent.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/9b0a44ccf18017482bf7418846333ac1.poster.avif?t=1725030021\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/9b0a44ccf18017482bf7418846333ac1.webm?t=1725030021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/9b0a44ccf18017482bf7418846333ac1.mp4?t=1725030021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collecting Relics</h2>Each run is unique with hundreds of different relic combinations to experiment with from filling the skies with gunfire and mines, to creating elite attack squadrons capable of defeating 5 times their number in flight.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/1fd1de979183079c6c86d15b98c262b1.poster.avif?t=1725030021\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/1fd1de979183079c6c86d15b98c262b1.webm?t=1725030021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/1fd1de979183079c6c86d15b98c262b1.mp4?t=1725030021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beyond the Run</h2>Progression isn't limited to a single run as, at the end of every run, you will gain research which will unlock new relics for future runs, and each achievement you complete will unlock a modifier that you can activate to change some core part of future runs.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/9297ac7426c0a01d5057179cdeb33afe.poster.avif?t=1725030021\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/9297ac7426c0a01d5057179cdeb33afe.webm?t=1725030021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/9297ac7426c0a01d5057179cdeb33afe.mp4?t=1725030021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
